</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
MORE ON AEROBICS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Apropos the furor surrounding Susan Littwin's humorous criticism of men in 
aerobics classes, "Walk Like a Man" (Feb. 5): Erik Fair's rebuttal "Sex and 
Exercise" (April 2) was a cute attempt, but his caustic remarks merely prove 
Littwin's point that men think they set all the standards. 
</P>
<P>
MARGOT DOKKEN 
</P>
<P>
Redondo Beach 
</P>
