<HEADLINE>
<P>
SENIOR YEARS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Thanks for your articles and separate section ("The Special Years, 50 and 
Beyond: The Time of Your Life," May 4) that highlighted the 50-plus age group 
-- I'm one of them. 
</P>
<P>
I really feel it is a neglected group of people, and the marketing people, if 
no one else, are missing a lot by not noticing us or mentioning our existence. 
I also felt your statistics about growing older were heartening and less 
negative and frightening than many I've seen. We can all use that good 
information. 
</P>
<P>
MRS. D. BARKER 
</P>
<P>
Escondido 
</P>
