<HEADLINE>
<P>
ADDING INSULT TO INJURY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I found a few interesting points in the story on John Mack. During his 
sentencing, Mack was described as being under "intense psychological pressure 
from 72-hour workweeks and a failing 3-week-old marriage." I also noticed that 
currently Mack is "handling major responsibilities under considerable 
pressure." 
</P>
<P>
KEVIN STEINFELD 
</P>
<P>
Seal Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
