<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE BARGAIN CORNER: CAR-RENTAL DISCOUNTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JACK ADLER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Budget Rent A Car of Southern California is offering renters a coupon booklet 
with discounts on car and truck rentals, sightseeing attractions, hotels and 
restaurants. 
</P>
<P>
You can get the booklet with a minimum rental of one day at any of Budget's 87 
locations from Santa Barbara to San Diego. 
</P>
<P>
Car-rental discounts are for the following rental after the one that qualifies 
for the booklet. But you can rent a car for one day, take it back and get a $10 
discount off the next day's rental, according to a Budget spokeswoman. 
</P>
<P>
Coupons also are provided on the same basis for Sears Rent A Car both in 
Southern California and Las Vegas. Cars supplied are Budget's autos, the Budget 
spokeswoman said. 
</P>
<P>
Most of the discounts expire Nov. 1. Some extend to the end of the year. The 
booklets contain a tear-off identification card that must be presented with the 
coupons. 
</P>
<P>
Restaurant coupons are two-for-one offers, but at some establishments 
restrictions apply. Check the reverse side of the coupon. Some, for instance, 
state that "tipping should be 15% to 20% of total check before discount," while 
another indicates that a "gratuity of 15% of total bill before discount will be 
added to your check." 
</P>
<P>
Attractions offering discounts include Knott's Berry Farm, the San Diego Zoo, 
San Diego Wild Animal Park, Queen Mary and the Spruce Goose/Port of Long Beach. 
At Knott's Berry Farm you can get $4 off for up to six admissions. 
</P>
<P>
Invader Cruises, which runs narrated sailings out of San Diego Bay, provides 
two free fares when you buy two harbor-cruise tickets. 
</P>
<P>
Among the hotels offering discounts are Vagabond Inns, Red Lion Inns in Costa 
Mesa and Ontario, the Radisson Plaza Hotel in Manhattan Beach, Newport Beach 
and Long Beach Airport Marriotts, the Newporter Resort, San Diego Princess, 
Omni San Diego, Embassy Suites in Irvine and San Diego, and the Palm Springs 
Biltmore. Los Angeles properties include the Sheraton Universal, Westin 
Bonaventure and Biltmore. 
</P>
<P>
At some of the hotels, discounts are 50% off regular rates, or 10% off any 
special promotional room rate, whichever provides the greater discount. Rooms 
are on a space-available basis. Reservations are generally required, and you 
should indicate that you will be using the discount coupon. Some properties 
have maximum-stay limitations. 
</P>
<P>
For more information, call Budget Rent A Car at (800) 527-0700. JACK ADLER 
</P>
</TEXT>
