<HEADLINE>
<P>
SCHOOL ASSIGNMENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Students graduating from McKinley Elementary School will attend Lincoln Middle 
School starting in the fall, rather than John Adams Middle School. 
</P>
<P>
The Santa Monica-Malibu School Board voted unanimously Monday to make McKinley 
a feeder school to Lincoln. In addition to McKinley, Franklin and Roosevelt 
Elementary Schools are feeder schools to Lincoln. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA051489-0127 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 56903 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 14, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
