In the May 14 article, "Riccardo Muti: In Music's Fast Lane," the designer of 
the new Philadelphia Orchestra concert hall was misidentified. The design is by 
the architectural firm of Venturi, Rauch and Scott Brown. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
