</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
CEMETERIES; MURDERS -- PHILIPPINES; COMMUNIST PARTY -- PHILIPPINES; GUERRILLAS 
-- PHILIPPINES; NEW PEOPLE'S ARMY (PHILIPPINES); PHILIPPINES -- REVOLTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA051489-0160 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 56984 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 14, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
