Photo, Left: Sun Yat-sen.; Photo, Below: Army of the Russian Revolution, 1918.; 
Photo, Above: Nationalist troops in Shanghai.; Photo, Left: Chiang Kai-shek.; 
Photo, Below: Chinese officers in Long March with Deng Xiaoping, far right.; 
