Anastas Mikoyan (right) and Gen. N. V. Roschin (left of Chou En-lai).; Photo, 
Below: Mao Tse-tung on the march against the Nationalists, 1947.; Photo, Mao 
Tse-tung and Nikita Khrushchev inspect honor guard in Beijing, 1959.; Photo, 
Above: Soviet guards along border with China.; Photo, Below: Alexei Kosygin 
greets Chou En-lai.; Photo, Top: Nixon with Chou En-lai in Beijing; Photo, 
Below: Deng Xiaoping with senators in Washington.; Photo, Top: Soviet tank in 
Kabul, Afghanistan.; Photo, Bottom: Bombing near Phnom Penh, Cambodia.; Photo, 
Left: Mikhail Gorbachev; Photo, Below: Soviet soldier gives a thumb-up during 
Soviet withdrawal from Afghanistan.; Chart, Years of Friendship, Years of 
Stress, PATRICIA MITCHELL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
